{"tid":2186584,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，係”毒撚”唔係”毒 男”啊屌","createTime":"2020-09-03T05:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T07:35:13.000Z","uid":366192,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2e676db9dcf57f127577198bd7f0867d8f5a1929","tid":2186584,"uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:16:30.000Z","msg":"未有account之前成日見到你哋咁打<br />\n冇用㗎，要激嬲毒男要打<span class=\"red\">毒撚</span>先得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係有啲無謂嘅執著但係如果同佢哋罵戰打毒男<br />\n佢哋會覺得有少少唔知做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然係事實嚟不過整碎到佢哋玻璃心真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Fucking Toxic Penis spreading poison everywhere~~&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;Wait what you are Toxic Penis? Then why are you out here?&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;Omg another Toxic Penis paying moeney to buy photo's of electronic chickens&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;Go back to your Patreon Toxic Penis, Jable tv is for human.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n不過有樣嘢想講<br />\n試過幾次被毒撚話我被女神Brainwashed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後我唔需要同佢哋理性討論<br />\n淨係覆佢&rdquo;A locked up fucked up Toxic Penis saying people outside the wall being brainwashed? How sarcastic&rdquo;<br />\n已經夠曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsorly41999因為而家咁多嘢發生好多負面情緒<br />\n只係分享下我點樣發洩壓力啫<br />\n對住佢哋發洩完之後特別爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔好畀位佢哋攻擊或者中佢哋嘅伏<br />\n對住毒撚口交要有特別嘅技巧<br />\n記得等毒撚爆粗先好搶道德高地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多數會用殘體爆粗<br />\n到時可以用英文翻譯畀外國人睇佢哋幾低賤(如果YouTube comment section)<br />\n<br />\n如果想我分享多啲經驗/戰術我得閒可以講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時發覺啲毒撚英文又幾好，學到啲新嘅生字下次罵戰又可以用<br />\n其實想英文進步，罵戰都係一個唔錯嘅選擇<br />\nSorly again41999<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f89198fbbe7a8f128ffd32380764693fb005e29","tid":2186584,"uid":135081,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:18:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">&rdquo;A locked up fucked up Toxic Penis saying people outside the wall being brainwashed? How sarcastic&rdquo;</span><br />\n小妹wet哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d0346ef8e0b37a2f73905a4ccee75c8f77ffbb5","tid":2186584,"uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d8d7c8f44e1c9c0776343447e27a07f6e736d3","tid":2186584,"uid":320293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:19:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8500eed707b3af90ab80a198ddc8f22ff1985be","tid":2186584,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:36:26.000Z","msg":"唔該借個位嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n實用 post ,樓主可唔可以置頂？唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係想保護自己同埋身邊嘅人？即刻入嚟睇吓!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2185179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2185179</a>"},{"pid":"eb5c62f2f255eebfaae9930997518f8104bc873f","tid":2186584,"uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8500eed707b3af90ab80a198ddc8f22ff1985be","tid":2186584,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:36:26.000Z","msg":"唔該借個位嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n實用 post ,樓主可唔可以置頂？唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真